name: SNOW LEOPARD - ENDANGERED SPECIES SERIES #1 of 200
description: A series of 200 NFTs on Hic Et Nunc by Marc Craig of Endangered Species from countries around the world. The Snow Leopard is listed as Vulnerable on the IUCN Red List because the global population is estimated to number fewer than 10,000 mature individuals and is expected to decline about 10% by 2040.
